#: pika-backup/src/widget/dialog/unmount_archives.ui:34
msgid ""
"The listed archives failed to close. Files within these archives must no "
"longer be open with other applications. Folders in within these archives "
"must no longer be open in browsers."
msgstr ""
"A felsorolt archívumokat nem sikerült lezárni. Az ezen archívumokon belüli fáj"
